data.description: PRICE REDUCED TO SELL! WELCOME HOME to the perfect ENTERTAINING HOME! Come see this beautiful FULLY REMODELED GULF ACCESS home on an OVERSIZED PROPERTY in highly reputable RIVER FOREST community! Home offers so much square footage for the price! Over 2300 sq ft! Plenty of room for your guests! TWO SPACIOUS bedrooms & ONE bath on one side of the home, LARGE Master Bed & Master Bath and 4th bedroom on other side. ALL BATHROOMS HAVE ALSO BEEN FULLY REMODELED! Home features a SEPARATE living room & dining room, which is perfect for the holidays & parties & SLIDERS opening up to the GAME/ MEDIA OR OFFICE!  The HUGE kitchen has been FULLY remodeled with NEW cabinetry, GORGEOUS GRANITE counter tops, NEW STAINLESS APPLIANCES & ISLAND with a SUPER LARGE breakfast bar!! Walk out to the screened lanai & RELAX in your PRIVATE OASIS BACKYARD! Backyard has lots of mature foliage for privacy & walk to your boat in your own backyard! Get ready to RELAX on the water in your WATERFRONT PARTY OASIS, with plenty of seating & provides electric for your lighting & can be fully closed up. Even room for your RV w/50 AMP POWER! BRAND NEW ROOF 2022, NEW A/C, WATER HTR 2022! COME SEE THIS BEAUTIFUL HOME!
